-Powered Disaster Management System   |   Node.js, Express.js, MongoDB, REST APIs, JWT, Cloudinary\n\u2022 Developed a backend-driven disaster management platform for reporting emergencies and coordinating rescue \noperations.\n\u2022 Built secure REST APIs for user authentication, disaster reporting, live location sharing, and donation management.\n\u2022 Implemented JWT authentication with Role-Based Access Control (RBAC) to secure sensitive endpoints.\n\u2022 Integrated Cloudinary for image and video uploads and used MongoDB for efficient, flexible data storage.\n\u2022 Architected the backend for scalability with input validation, structured error handling, and API documentation.\nCERTIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Python and Raspberry Pi Workshop \u2014 May 2024\n\u2022 MERN Stack Certification \u2014 Blue Witcher\nEDUCATION", "embedding": [-0.07361659407615662, -0.007360741030424833, -0.0025782620068639517, -0.003448566421866417, 0.004245415795594454, -0.06002788245677948, -0.05741377919912338, 0.031461164355278015, -0.04921455308794975, 0.011245561763644218, -0.058413345366716385, 0.05385642871260643, 0.07293510437011719, -0.04160492122173309, 0.033102963119745255, 0.03458414226770401, 0.04114827513694763, -0.015125184319913387, 0.014218009077012539, -0.07199893891811371, -0.1018671914935112, 0.012693415395915508, -0.007216138765215874, 0.04552515596151352, -0.003192008240148425, 0.02101888321340084, -0.00019030712428502738, -0.009182804264128208, -0.05203885957598686, -0.05379677563905716, 0.009338629432022572, -0.04804592579603195, -0.03803185373544693, 0.08146370947360992, -0.07578250020742416, 0.033292438834905624, 0.07952362298965454, -0.10766076296567917, -0.07364398241043091, -0.12516716122627258, -0.03350045531988144, -0.07320814579725266, -0.09371159970760345, 0.022632218897342682, 0.0011683311313390732, -0.021124079823493958, -0.017122337594628334, -0.029999135062098503, 0.0011939003597944975, -0.006295066326856613, 0.06242946535348892, -0.07569732517004013, -0